tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE player_statistics (
    player_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    player_name VARCHAR,
    win_count INT,
    loss_count INT,
    kill_count INT
);

CREATE TABLE player_kills (
    kill_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    player_id UUID,
    match_id UUID,
    kill_count INT,
    kill_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE players (
    player_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    player_name VARCHAR(50),
    win_count INT,
    loss_count INT
)

CREATE TABLE matches (
    match_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    match_date DATE,
    player_id UUID,
    opponent_id UUID,
    match_result VARCHAR(10)
)

CREATE TABLE kills (
    kill_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    match_id UUID,
    player_id UUID,
    opponent_id UUID,
    kill_timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE teams (
    team_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    team_name VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE match_players (
    match_id UUID,
    player_id UUID,
    team_id UUID
)

CREATE TABLE player_stats (
    player_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    win_loss_ratio FLOAT,
    total_kills INT
)
